# App-generated process-docs convention file (written into WORKING folders by
# ensureAgentsFile); not a repo artifact — appears here only if the repo root is
# opened as a working folder.
AGENTS.md

# AI-agent overlays generated into working folders — may hold private/team/personal
# notes. `*.local` above does NOT catch these (they end in .md). Covers the team
# overlay (AGENTS.local.md), the pre-v2 backup, and personal overlays (AGENTS.<name>.md).
AGENTS.local.md
AGENTS.*.md
# Personal, machine-local overrides (never shared).
CLAUDE.local.md

# Internal dev artifacts — kept locally, never published
CLAUDE.md
docs/superpowers/
docs/QA-colaboracion.md
